text.tspan: Assurance and Joy of Salvation—A Complete Work
The law of life from our spirit within,
Saves us from death and the bondage of sin;
His divine life is forever increased,
His divine life is forever increased...
The divine Trinity spreads through our soul,
To saturate our whole being, life’s goal;
We become members, the Body of Christ,
Built up together by Christ’s saving life,
Built up together by Christ’s saving life...
Christ’s saving life when expressed in each town,
Strengthens the saints causing grace to abound;
And by the reigning in life every church
Is blent together, and Satan is crushed,
Is blent together and Satan is crushed...
